videos.description: Auburn's T.J  Dunans knocks the ball away before finishing the dunk on the other end.
videos.headline: Dunans pokes the ball lose and throws it down on the other end

videos.description: Florida's John Egbunu beats two Auburn players for the offensive rebound and dunks it down.
videos.headline: Egbunu grabs the offensive rebound and dunks it down

videos.description: Auburn's Austin Wiley grabs the offensive rebound before powering to the rim for the dunk
videos.headline: Wiley overpowers Florida before throwing down a ferocious dunk

videos.description: After Florida's John Egbunu dunks it down, Austin Wiley responds immediately for Auburn.
videos.headline: Egbunu dunks on Auburn, Wiley responds with a dunk of his own

videos.description: John Egbunu grabs the offensive rebound off a Canyon Barry miss and dunks it down.
videos.headline: Egbunu throws down his third dunk of the 1st half

videos.description: Bryce Brown throws up the lob for LaRon Smith. Smith throws it down.
videos.headline: Brown finds Smith for the alley-oop.

videos.description: Going into the half tied, Bruce Pearl says Auburn must attack inside and continue to execute if they want to win.
videos.headline: Auburn Head Coach Bruce Pearl says team must continue to execute in 2nd half

videos.description: Anfernee McLemore catches the ball inside and powers his way to the rim for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: McLemore overpowers defender for the two-handed jam

videos.description: Florida's Devin Robinson throws down a ferocious putback dunk after Kasey Hill misses the layup.
videos.headline: Robinson obliterates the rim with a ferocious putback dunk

videos.description: John Egbunu leaves the game with apparent knee injury. He would not return.
videos.headline: John Egbunu leaves the game with apparent knee injury

videos.description: After putting up a record 114 points, Mike White says Florida's unselfish play and shooting were key.
videos.headline: Florida Head Coach Mike White credits victory to unselfish play and good shooting
